而说唱歌手的律师则因“无情地提出攻击性动议”而受到批评。</p><p> 12 月 8 日，据报道，Jay-Z（真名肖恩·卡特） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/with-legal-jay-z-accused-of-raping-13-year-old-girl-with-diddy-lawsuit-reveals-3820201">在一场诉讼中被点名，该诉讼指控说唱歌手和迪迪（真名肖恩·库姆斯）在 2000 年强奸了一名 13 岁女孩</a>。</p><p>在通过 Roc Nation 发表的一份声明中，卡特称这些指控“本质上令人发指”，并将其斥为“勒索企图”，并向<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jay-z-seeks-dismissal-of-diddy-lawsuit-this-is-a-shakedown-3820591">法院提交了一封信函，寻求驳回诉讼，</a>同时坚称自己无罪。库姆斯还否认原告的说法。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/jay-z-accuser-remain-anonymous-sexual-assault-lawsuit-1235214055/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《滚石》</i></a>报道，这封信还试图透露原告的身份，但在周四（12 月 26 日）的裁决中，法官阿娜丽莎·托雷斯宣布，该女子可以匿名审理此案。</p><p>法官在做出决定时指出了“因素的权重”，包括索赔的“高度敏感和极其个人化”的性质，认为这“有利于允许原告保持匿名，至少在诉讼的这个阶段是这样” ”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3824660" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3824660" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3824660" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jay-Z.-CREDIT_-Gilbert-Flores_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jay-Z.-CREDIT_-Gilbert-Flores_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jay-Z.-CREDIT_-Gilbert-Flores_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jay-Z.-CREDIT_-Gilbert-Flores_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jay-Z.-CREDIT_-Gilbert-Flores_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jay-Z.-CREDIT_-Gilbert-Flores_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jay-Z.-CREDIT_-Gilbert-Flores_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3824660" class="wp-caption-text">杰伊-Z。图片来源：Gi